---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="Contact Us - Online Ruler">
  <h1 class="text-[32px] md:text-[40px] font-semibold tracking-tight-apple mb-6">Contact Us</h1>
  
  <p>We would love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about calibrating your device, a feature request, or just want to say hello, our team is always ready to assist.</p>

  <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight-apple mt-6 mb-2">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>For general inquiries, support, or feedback, please email us at:</p>
  <p class="font-mono bg-canvas-parchment p-3 rounded-md border border-hairline inline-block mt-2">yahkashyap.freelancing@gmail.com</p>

  <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight-apple mt-6 mb-2">Bug Reports</h2>
  <p>If you have encountered an issue with the ruler's accuracy or a display bug on a specific device, please include the following information in your email:</p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 flex flex-col gap-1 mt-2">
    <li>Your device model (e.g., iPhone 14 Pro, Dell 27" Monitor)</li>
    <li>Your operating system and browser</li>
    <li>A brief description of the problem</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-8 text-body-muted">We typically respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours during regular business days.</p>
</PageLayout>
